SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend the Floor Substitute for House Bill No. 3000 (#3949) as follows:
1. On Page 6, Line 22, by striking after the word “Act” and before the word “be”, the word “shall”,
and inserting the word “may”;
2. On Page 6, Line 22, by inserting after the word “Oklahoma” and before the word “and”, the
words “or the State Board of Cosmetology and Barbering”;
3. On Page 12, Line 21 1/2 , by inserting a new subsection to read as follows:
“ G. On or before January 1, 2028, the State Board of Cosmetology and Barbering shall remove two
(2) employee licensing positions, and such positions shall be replaced by two (2) employee facility
inspector positions.”
